  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个安全架构的流程图，从OAuth2认证开始，经过防火墙，然后进入一个加密决策节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，OAuth2作为入口节点，然后连到防火墙。这个加密节点是菱形判断框吗？它分出几条分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，加密节点是决策点。它要分出三条路径：第一条到零信任架构，第二条到入侵检测系统，第三条回到加密模块本身做循环处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "三条分支我记下了。防火墙到加密节点之间的连线需要标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Firewall",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "防火墙到加密节点不用标注，但OAuth2到防火墙那条线要写上\"Get money\"，表示获取资源的意思。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加\"Get money\"标注。那三条分支分别用什么标注区分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分别用\"One\"、\"Two\"、\"Three\"标注，对应零信任、入侵检测和加密循环这三个方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成，三条分支标注分别是\"One\"到零信任，\"Two\"到入侵检测，\"Three\"回到加密模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我看看...等等，第三条分支的目标节点名称是不是有问题？加密决策节点指向的应该是另一个加密处理模块，不是决策节点自己。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "发现了，我之前把第三条线连回同一个加密决策节点了。应该新建一个加密处理模块作为目标，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，需要区分清楚：菱形的是加密决策节点，矩形的是具体的加密处理模块。这样结构才合理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复。现在流程是：OAuth2认证→防火墙→加密决策→分三支：零信任、入侵检测、加密处理模块。整个安全流程图完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
